  "text": "With the previous algorithm, we can predict label c i and its probability p i at each sequence position i. We introduce a score s i which is computed as [CITATION_1] gave a rigorous definition of maximal scoring segment (MSS) and a linear algorithm to find all of them. By default, dna-brnn takes an MSS longer than 50bp as a satellite segment. The use of MSS effectively clusters fragmented satellite predictions and improves the accuracy in practice.",
